main repo clone

Clone a repository

USAGE:
    main repo clone [OPTIONS] <URL>

ARGUMENTS:
        <URL>
            Repository URL

OPTIONS:
    -h, --help
            Show help message and exit.
    -V, --version
            Show version and exit.
        --completions <bash,zsh,fish>
            Generate shell completions.
        --depth <U32>
            Clone depth (shallow clone)
    -b, --branch <STRING>
            Branch to clone
